##Task-2 List comprehension problems
# a. square of a number(1-10)
square=[x**2 for x in range(1,11)]
print(square)

#b. Extract even number from list
numbers=[12,1,15,17,14,18,19,21,22,24,18]
even_num=[num for num in numbers if num%2==0]
print(even_num)

# c.Convert list of strings to uppercase
words=["Starcke","June","system","crore"]
words_upper=[w.upper() for w in words]
print(words_upper)
